紅潤，臉形略微浮腫，招牌尖下巴依舊醒目，美貌不減。<br />\n<br />\nBonnie 透露參加遊艇活動巧遇張柏芝，對方還帶著小兒子 Quintus 同行，據香港《蘋果日報》報導，被問到張柏芝是否生第三胎？ Bonnie 表示自己真的不清楚，「看她今天狀態，我認為她不是剛生完Baby，因為沒道理這麼快出門吹風」。<br />\n<br />\n至於張柏芝是否與新加坡富豪交往？ Bonnie 透露從沒聽說張柏芝有新對象，對於張柏芝被指外貌比先前圓潤？ Bonnie 則認為應是她之前弄傷十字韌帶，已有一段時間沒滑水的原因，間接替好友澄清懷孕一事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小美覺得單野好鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 實屬無稽之談"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"同呢2個3p,我ok"},{"pid":"54f1882b3d7deb9d109aa5968947bb238c16319d","tid":925690,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"正咗，出道肥肥哋嗰陣咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ec733f30ddfe2c1cc6f86572b42c4738a765fa","tid":925690,"uid":17545,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"96db3bd405e198367f1536dcbd6834759d62c605","tid":925690,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22784f6dc5bab91dbd2a21a29175e6f13de29239","tid":925690,"uid":17545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bf5078131f9bd3339d55e487790e71be478faa4","tid":925690,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"黎姿（已改名）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:16:57.000Z","msg":"馬黎珈而！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T03:20:57.000Z","msg":"個名勁有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T05:18:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新名勁娘喎<br />\n<br />\n舊名個姿 令人聯想起風姿綽約 黎姿同荔枝差唔多音 令人聯想到喜啖荔枝既楊貴妃 <br />\n<br />\n新名珈而 個名乍聽上嚟勁普通 個珈字又唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hk